author: By RYAN TRARES Daily Journal
title: Indiana student creates grocery service to aid the homebound
description: GREENWOOD, Ind. (AP) — Under a statewide stay-at-home orders, people are required to stay home unless they need to make essential trips, including buying groceries.
content:
